    ShowMgr -->|Show Configuration| AMTS
    AMTS -->|Config Status| ShowMgr

    %% Secretary flows
    Secretary -->|Role Management<br/>Show Setup| AMTS
    AMTS -->|Sales Reports<br/>Confirmations| Secretary

